01216                 YY_CURRENT_BUFFER_LVALUE->yy_ch_buf = (char *) yyrealloc((void *) YY_CURRENT_BUFFER_LVALUE->yy_ch_buf,new_size  );
01217                 if ( ! YY_CURRENT_BUFFER_LVALUE->yy_ch_buf )
01218                         YY_FATAL_ERROR( "out of dynamic memory in yy_get_next_buffer()" );

01222         YY_CURRENT_BUFFER_LVALUE->yy_ch_buf[(yy_n_chars)] = YY_END_OF_BUFFER_CHAR;
01223         YY_CURRENT_BUFFER_LVALUE->yy_ch_buf[(yy_n_chars) + 1] = YY_END_OF_BUFFER_CHAR;
01224 
01225         (yytext_ptr) = &YY_CURRENT_BUFFER_LVALUE->yy_ch_buf[0];

01287     static void yyunput (int c, register char * yy_bp )
01288 {
01289         register char *yy_cp;
01290     
01291     yy_cp = (yy_c_buf_p);
01292 
01293         /* undo effects of setting up yytext */
01294         *yy_cp = (yy_hold_char);
01295 
01296         if ( yy_cp < YY_CURRENT_BUFFER_LVALUE->yy_ch_buf + 2 )
01297                 { /* need to shift things up to make room */
01298                 /* +2 for EOB chars. */
01299                 register int number_to_move = (yy_n_chars) + 2;
01300                 register char *dest = &YY_CURRENT_BUFFER_LVALUE->yy_ch_buf[
01301                                         YY_CURRENT_BUFFER_LVALUE->yy_buf_size + 2];
01302                 register char *source =
01303                                 &YY_CURRENT_BUFFER_LVALUE->yy_ch_buf[number_to_move];
01304 
01305                 while ( source > YY_CURRENT_BUFFER_LVALUE->yy_ch_buf )
01306                         *--dest = *--source;
01307 
01308                 yy_cp += (int) (dest - source);
01309                 yy_bp += (int) (dest - source);
01310                 YY_CURRENT_BUFFER_LVALUE->yy_n_chars =
01311                         (yy_n_chars) = YY_CURRENT_BUFFER_LVALUE->yy_buf_size;
01312 
01313                 if ( yy_cp < YY_CURRENT_BUFFER_LVALUE->yy_ch_buf + 2 )
01314                         YY_FATAL_ERROR( "flex scanner push-back overflow" );
01315                 }
01316 
01317         *--yy_cp = (char) c;
01318 
01319         (yytext_ptr) = yy_bp;
01320         (yy_hold_char) = *yy_cp;
01321         (yy_c_buf_p) = yy_cp;
01322 }

01573 void yypush_buffer_state (YY_BUFFER_STATE new_buffer )

01619 /* Allocates the stack if it does not exist.
01620  *  Guarantees space for at least one push.
01621  */
01622 static void yyensure_buffer_stack (void)
01623 {
01624         int num_to_alloc;
01625     
01626         if (!(yy_buffer_stack)) {
01627 
01628                 /* First allocation is just for 2 elements, since we don't know if this
01629                  * scanner will even need a stack. We use 2 instead of 1 to avoid an
01630                  * immediate realloc on the next call.
01631          */
01632                 num_to_alloc = 1;
01633                 (yy_buffer_stack) = (struct yy_buffer_state**)yyalloc
01634                                                                 (num_to_alloc * sizeof(struct yy_buffer_state*)
01635                                                                 );
01636                 if ( ! (yy_buffer_stack) )
01637                         YY_FATAL_ERROR( "out of dynamic memory in yyensure_buffer_stack()" );
01638                                                                   
01639                 memset((yy_buffer_stack), 0, num_to_alloc * sizeof(struct yy_buffer_state*));
01640                                 
01641                 (yy_buffer_stack_max) = num_to_alloc;
01642                 (yy_buffer_stack_top) = 0;
01643                 return;
01644         }
01645 
01646         if ((yy_buffer_stack_top) >= ((yy_buffer_stack_max)) - 1){
01647 
01648                 /* Increase the buffer to prepare for a possible push. */
01649                 int grow_size = 8 /* arbitrary grow size */;
01650 
01651                 num_to_alloc = (yy_buffer_stack_max) + grow_size;
01652                 (yy_buffer_stack) = (struct yy_buffer_state**)yyrealloc
01653                                                                 ((yy_buffer_stack),
01654                                                                 num_to_alloc * sizeof(struct yy_buffer_state*)
01655                                                                 );
01656                 if ( ! (yy_buffer_stack) )
01657                         YY_FATAL_ERROR( "out of dynamic memory in yyensure_buffer_stack()" );
01658 
01659                 /* zero only the new slots.*/
01660                 memset((yy_buffer_stack) + (yy_buffer_stack_max), 0, grow_size * sizeof(struct yy_buffer_state*));
01661                 (yy_buffer_stack_max) = num_to_alloc;
01662         }
01663 }
